'''罗杰·戈斯登'''（{{lang-en|Roger Gordon Gosden}}，1948年9月23日-）是一位美英双重国籍的生殖科学和科普作家，其研究方向为[[女性|女性]][[生殖醫學|生殖醫學]]和[[卵巢|卵巢]][[生理学|生理学]]，主要科普作品有《欺骗时间：科学、性与衰老》（''Cheating Time: Science, Aex and Ageing''）、《设计婴儿：生殖技术的美丽新世界》（''Designing Babies: The Brave New World of Reproductive Technology''）等。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://issuu.com/darwinian/docs/darwinian_summer_2007/10|title=New York alumni gathering|last=|first=|date=2007|newspaper=The Darwinian|access-date=2017-02-06|work=|editor-last=Prentice|editor-first=Andrew|via=Issuu.com|editor-last2=Smith|editor-first2=Sophia|editor-last3=Jebb|editor-last4=Hawkes|editor-first3=Richard|editor-first4=Dean|display-editors=2}}</ref><ref name=Gosden1974>{{Cite thesis|url=http://ulmss-newton.lib.cam.ac.uk/vwebv/holdingsInfo?bibId=8858|title=Reproductive senescence in female rodents|last=Gosden|first=R.G.|publisher=University of Cambridge Department of Physiology|date=1974-05-21}}</ref><ref name=Edwards>{{cite journal|last1=Johnson|first1=MH|title=Robert Edwards: the path to IVF|journal=Reproductive Biomedicine Online|date=August 2011|volume=23|issue=2|pages=245–62|pmid=21680248|pmc=3171154|doi=10.1016/j.rbmo.2011.04.010}}</ref>
